channel.title: 508 client problem
channel.description:
Hi, I got a problem: When i start my 508server, and then start up the 508 IP changing client, after i put in my hamachi ip, it keeps saying: Connecting to update server.
And in the cmd screen it says: error_game_js5connect
So i don't know how to fix this.
I installed Titana cache, and i putted in 508 in my Titana cache, and in my C:\ , so i don't know why it wont work.... Plz help me, maybe it's just an easy awnser... Thanks already, Nick.
